OL,3,CHospital bosses believe they are
OL,4,Chalfway to plugging #80m deficit
OL,6,FNewcastle hospital bosses believe they
OL,7,Fare halfway to plugging a #80 million
OL,8,Fcash deficit.
OL,10,FThe which runs the Royal Victoria
OL,11,FInfirmary and Freeman Hospital, warned
OL,12,Ftwo months ago that it was failing to
OL,13,Fmake sufficient savings and as a
OL,14,Fresult was facing serious financial
OL,15,Ftrouble.
OL,17,FIn March it was reported that had the
OL,18,FTrust continued spending at its
OL,19,Fprevious rate, it could run out of
OL,20,Fmoney by September.
