OL,3,CHospital bosses believe they are
OL,4,Chalfway to plugging #80m deficit
OL,6,FSir James Mackey, the Trust's chief
OL,7,Fexecutive said bosses were working
OL,8,F"rapidly to address that situation".
OL,10,Fhave now been told that cost-cutting
OL,11,Fplans have managed to slash the
OL,12,Fhospitals' estimated deficit for 2024/
OL,13,F25 in half, from #80 million to #40
OL,14,Fmillion.
OL,16,FRob Harrison, the Trust's new managing
OL,17,Fdirector, told the local authority
OL,18,Fthat bosses were aiming to get close
OL,19,Fto a balanced budget but with "clear
OL,20,Ffocus on doing it without affecting
OL,21,Fdirect patient care".
