OL,3,CHospital bosses believe they are
OL,4,Chalfway to plugging #80m deficit
OL,6,FThe problem is said to have arisen as
OL,7,Fthe Trust was meant to deliver #33
OL,8,Fmillion in recurrent savings during
OL,9,Fthe previous financial year.
OL,11,FIt actually only managed to find #6
OL,12,Fmillion through of repeating year-on-
OL,13,Fyear savings and was instead forced to
OL,14,Frely on one-off cuts to try and
OL,15,Fbalance the books.
