OL,3,CHospital bosses believe they are
OL,4,Chalfway to plugging #80m deficit
OL,6,FThe challenging financial situation
OL,7,Fcame amid a backdrop of a damning Care
OL,8,FQuality Commission (CQC) report which
OL,9,Fdowngraded Newcastle Hospitals from
OL,10,F'outstanding' to 'requires
OL,11,Fimprovement' earlier this year.
OL,13,FMr Harrison said on Thursday: "We are
OL,14,Freally focused on doing everything we
OL,15,Fcan to protect frontline services.
OL,16,FThere are efficiencies we can make in
OL,17,Fclinical areas, but that is not the
OL,18,Fsame as cutting those services."
