OL,4,Chalfway to plugging #80m deficit
OL,6,FHe added: "We are looking at the
OL,7,Festate we use. Buildings cost money
OL,8,Fand if there are opportunities to
OL,9,Fchange how many buildings we use and
OL,10,Fkeep their services, but run them in a
OL,11,Fdifferent way, then we are going to
OL,12,Flook at that."
